#L_D5_msg00=Attention, civilian ships, the system is under martial law. A special pass is required to move around freely.
#L_D5_ans00=I'm a free trader and I go where I please. Got it?
#L_D5_ans02=Officer, I quite get it and would be grateful to you, er, finanically, if you help us cross this system and jump to Al-Zed.
