#L_D5_msg12=Why do you even care about those rebels?
#L_D5_ans12=Just business, officer. You've scanned by cargo bay and can see what I'm carrying. They are willing to pay for it, and I'm willing to share.
#L_D5_msg22=Share?.. Well, we could use some cash right now... All right, I'll take you to the Al-Zed portal for 50,000 credits.
